com.stripe.android.view

Class AddPaymentMethodActivityStarter

  • ActivityStarter
    • com.stripe.android.view.AddPaymentMethodActivityStarter

  • public class AddPaymentMethodActivityStarter
extends ActivityStarter

    A class to start class AddPaymentMethodActivity. Arguments for the activity can be specified with class AddPaymentMethodActivityStarter.Args and constructed with class Args.Builder.

    The result will be returned with request code REQUEST_CODE.
